room_title: Escape room "Escape to Earth!" by Escape SBC in Shreveport
room_description:
Founded on the Earth’s moon in 1997, Area 53 serves as the US Government’s premiere facility for testing the potential of powerful new technologies.  Leading the crew at Area 53 is Professor Darius Bishop.  His classified and top secret experiments don’t always work out as planned.  Something has gone terribly wrong in Area 53…

Can you and your team destroy Dr. Bishop’s mutant experiment gone wrong and save yourselves and the Earth?  The fate of the world depends on you…Can you complete this mission in the dark sector and Escape to Earth??
